## Anti-patterns (avoid)

❌ **Do not mix functional and style props inside `useProps`**

```typescript
// BAD
const { onClick, buttonProps, ...rest } = useProps(...);
```

❌ **Do not use ambiguous component ids**

```typescript
// BAD — too generic
useProps("Button", ...)
```

❌ **Do not omit meaningful `defaultStyleProps`**

```typescript
// BAD — empty defaults unless truly intentional
const props = useProps("Component", {}, props);
```

❌ **Do not duplicate theme configuration inline**

```typescript
// BAD — hard-coded instead of theme/useProps
<Button variant="light" fullWidth={true}>
```

